text: Peter James O'Brien may refer to: *James O'Brien (New Zealand politician) (1874–1947), New Zealand politician with the full name of Peter James O'Brien *Pete O'Brien (1890s second baseman) (1867–1937), American Major League Baseball player with the full name of Peter James O'Brien *Peter O'Brien (filmmaker) (born 1983), independent American filmmaker and author with the full name of Peter James O'Brien ==See also== *Peter O'Brien (disambiguation)
